.so fork.tmac
.SS ARGEATER_PROCESS
.PP
This function uses a copy of the command line arguments
.RI ( clones ),
and a map of actions
.RI ( map )
with which to match them, to easily access the users' command line
arguments.
.IP
.p_argeater_process
.PP
Make
.I clones
with the
.B CLONE_ARGS
macro and the
.I map
with the
.B INIT_MAP
macro.
.PP
The function returns
.B true if successful but terminates immediately and returns
.B false
for any error processing arguments.

